Package edu.kit.kastel.mcse.ardoco.core.model

Class ModelInstanceImpl

java.lang.Object
edu.kit.kastel.mcse.ardoco.core.model.ModelInstanceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ModelInstance
public class ModelInstanceImpl extends Object implements ModelInstance
This class represents an instance extracted from a model. The name of an instance (as well as the type) are splitted at spaces and can be seen as multiple names. Therefore, the longestName (and type) is the original name (type) of the instance.
